@startuml
left to right direction

AudioPlaybackService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioUploadService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioCatalogoService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioValidarService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioPlaybackService ..> [Componente Usuário]
AudioValidarService ..> [Componente Uploader] 
AudioUploadService ..> [Componente Uploader]
AudioCatalogoService ..> [Componente Usuário] : "buscarAudio()"
AudioCatalogoService ..> [Componente Usuário] : "listarAudioUploader()"
@enduml
